name: Fiery Panang chicken curry
description: Our spin on the spiced Malaysian classic hits your table as quick as a takeaway, but is lighter – with free-range chicken breast, spinach, juicy peppers and crunchy cashews.

name: Creamy coconut fish pie
description: Our decadent fish pie is a real crowd-pleaser, brimming with sustainably sourced fish chunks and lashings of coconut milk. We’ve snuck in healthy greens too: leafy spinach and green beans.

name: Chicken tikka masala
description: Free-range chicken breast, plump cherry tomatoes, spinach and velvety coconut milk: we’ve given this crowd-pleasing curry a Mindful Chef makeover. A sprinkling of moreish coconut chips adds crunch.

name: Veggie shepherd’s pie
description: Juicy mushrooms, earthy chestnuts, hearty beans – we’ve packed our meat-free spin on shepherd’s pie with all kinds of veg. It’s topped with a fluffy sweet potato mash.

name: Creamy lentil moussaka
description: Our plant-based moussaka is irresistible – starring cinnamon-spiced lentils, savoury tomato sauce and tender aubergine. You’ll go crazy for our vegan béchamel, made with creamy coconut.

name: Moroccan lamb shoulder tagine
description: Tender chunks of pasture-grazed British lamb coated in a Moroccan-style stew, fragranced by warm cinnamon and dried apricots. On the side: fluffy British quinoa, to soak up all that flavour.
